PROMPT FOR CREATING ARTIZEN ART CAFE WEBSITE

You are a senior website copywriter and conversion strategist.
Your task is to generate high-converting, benefit-driven website copy for a cafe.

Business Details:
Business Name:Artizen Art cafe
Location: Mumbai
Target Audience: people of any age group who love art and peaceful ambience
Unique Selling Proposition:cafe with art activities
Tone: [friendly/creative/exciting/curious/ confident-simple/more catch lines]
Key Services:veg food,deserts,non alcoholic drinks and art activities
Brand Personality:cozy and creative
Pricing Level: mid range with special discounts for children below 18
Special Features (if any): people can take their art work with them and charged photography services

Requirements:

1. Write clear, persuasive, real-world website copy.

2. Avoid generic AI language.

3. Use business-specific vocabulary.

4. Include strong, actionable CTAs.

5. Make content ready to paste into a real website.

6. Structure output into:

Homepage

Services Page (atleast 10 food dishes and 5-8 drinks)

3 CTA Sections (booking, trust, urgency/location)

Elaborative content for all sections

7. Tone must adapt based on business type.

8. Keep language natural, human, and customer-focused.

9.Add images and videos related to the requirements in the website.

10.Add neat and correct contact and address details

Provide a website copy set as per the given requirements.


